歐洲.name: Bosnia and Herzegovina
歐洲.chinese: 波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納

歐洲.name: Montenegro
歐洲.capital: Podgorica; note - Cetinje retains the status of "Old Royal Capital"

歐洲.name: Netherlands
歐洲.capital: Amsterdam; note - The Hague is the seat of government

歐洲.name: Ukraine
歐洲.capital: Kyiv (Kiev is the transliteration from Russian)

南亞.name: Sri Lanka
南亞.capital: Colombo (commercial capital); Sri Jayewardenepura Kotte (legislative capital)

東南亞.name: Myanmar
東南亞.capital: Rangoon (aka Yangon, continues to be recognized as the primary Burmese capital by the US Government); Nay Pyi Taw is the administrative capital

東南亞.name: Indonesia
東南亞.capital: Jakarta; note - Indonesian lawmakers on 18 January 2022 approved the relocation of the country’s capital from Jakarta to a site on the island of Borneo between Samarinda City and the port city of Balikpapan; Nusantara ("archipelago"), the name of the new capital, is expected to be established in August 2024

東南亞.name: Malaysia
東南亞.capital: Kuala Lumpur; note - nearby Putrajaya is referred to as a federal government administrative center but not the capital; Parliament meets in Kuala Lumpur

東亞.name: Korea, Rep.
東亞.capital: Seoul; note - Sejong, located some 120 km (75 mi) south of Seoul, serves as an administrative capital for segments of the South Korean Government

西亞.name: Israel
西亞.capital: Jerusalem; note - the US recognized Jerusalem as Israel’s capital in December 2017 without taking a position on the specific boundaries of Israeli sovereignty

中南美洲.name: Honduras
中南美洲.capital: Tegucigalpa; note - article eight of the Honduran constitution states that the twin cities of Tegucigalpa and Comayaguela, jointly, constitute the capital of the Republic of Honduras; however, virtually all governmental institutions are on the Tegucigalpa side, which in practical terms makes Tegucigalpa the capital

中南美洲.name: St. Kitts and Nevis
中南美洲.chinese: 聖克里斯多福及尼維斯

中南美洲.name: Bolivia
中南美洲.capital: La Paz (administrative capital); Sucre (constitutional [legislative and judicial] capital)

中南美洲.name: Chile
中南美洲.capital: Santiago; note - Valparaiso is the seat of the national legislature

大洋洲.name: Marshall Islands
大洋洲.capital: Majuro; note - the capital is an atoll of 64 islands; governmental buildings are housed on three fused islands on the eastern side of the atoll: Djarrit, Uliga, and Delap

大洋洲.name: Nauru
大洋洲.capital: no official capital; government offices in the Yaren District

大洋洲.name: Tuvalu
大洋洲.capital: Funafuti; note - the capital is an atoll of some 29 islets; administrative offices are in Vaiaku Village on Fongafale Islet

漠南非洲.name: Cote d'Ivoire
漠南非洲.capital: Yamoussoukro (legislative capital), Abidjan (administrative capital); note - although Yamoussoukro has been the official capital since 1983, Abidjan remains the administrative capital as well as the officially designated economic capital; the US, like other countries, maintains its Embassy in Abidjan

漠南非洲.name: Equatorial Guinea
漠南非洲.capital: Malabo; note - Malabo is on the island of Bioko; some months of the year, the government operates out of Bata on the mainland region.

漠南非洲.name: Eswatini
漠南非洲.capital: Mbabane (administrative capital); Lobamba (royal and legislative capital)

漠南非洲.name: South Africa
漠南非洲.capital: Pretoria (administrative capital); Cape Town (legislative capital); Bloemfontein (judicial capital)

漠南非洲.name: Tanzania
漠南非洲.capital: Dodoma; note - Dodoma was designated the national capital in 1996; Dar es Salaam, the original national capital, is the country's largest city and commercial center
